{
  "text": "Remark 8. Similar algorithms for approximating γ ± givenγ have been proposed in the literature [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] . However to our knowledge, this is the first analysis to establish an explicit convergence rate; see the discussion after Remark 2.11 in [CITATION_5] on this issue.",
